    "description": "Flife is more than just a game title; it encapsulates the fusion of 'Flip' and 'Knife' in its original meaning, but it also carries a profound message. When you combine 'F' and 'life,' it becomes a testament to the idea that as long as you persevere and keep trying, life can truly be fantastic. This is the profound experience I aim for players to immerse themselves in as they journey towards the conclusion of my game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExperience the challenge of climbing with a knife all the way to the top! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFlip your favorite knife to climb up dynamic landscapes. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n■ Flip your knife all the way to the top.<br />\r\n■ Millions of different knife customizations! <br />\r\n■ There is no save point. <br />\r\n■ Don't give up!",
